    "description": {
      "value": "<p>At 9th level, you can touch a metal or stone weapon (or up to 50 pieces of ammunition) as a <em>standard action</em>, giving it the <em>bane</em> property against any creature with the <em>earth</em> subtype, <em>oozes</em>, or <em>constructs</em> made of stone or metal, for 1 minute. You can use this ability once per day at 9th level, twice per day at 17th, and three times per day at 20th.</p>"
